FROM [reply] AS [rp.Replies]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [rp0].[id]
    FROM [comment] AS [rp0]
    LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [rp.user0] ON [rp0].[userId] = [rp.user0].[Id]

) AS [t] ON [rp.Replies].[commentId] = [t].[id]
ORDER BY [t].[id]" (0723d8ff)
